name: sharing is caring
description: "sharing is caring” Most Asian cultures talk about how they believe in serving others first before you serve yourself, and for centuries no matter which Asian household it’s believe a social norm. This piece talks about societal hospitality. The elements of this piece are , The fish being cleaned and prepared into sushi and sliced to precision. The noodles being picked up hot and ready to be served, The sauce as the delicate balance of flavour.
